metadata.purpose: Curated list for physical therapy, prehab, and rehab
excludedTypes: Advanced calisthenics (not suitable for injury recovery)
One-arm variations (too advanced for most rehab)

instructions.forAI: When generating exercise plans, ONLY use exercise names from this list. Use the exact "name" field. Do not make up exercise names.
instructions.matching: The exercise ID will be used to fetch GIFs from ExerciseDB API.
